These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, fonseca, old-henry
City: miami, hannover, new-york
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, february
House: victorian, gothic-revival, wooden
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
3 different pets are kept: snake, horse, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the snake is the german##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the italian and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is the colombian##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the victorian house##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Cigar          | fonseca       | old-henry    | blend         |
| City         | hannover    | new-york  | miami        |
| Birthday           | june | january   | february      |
| House   | gothic-revival        | wooden    | victorian       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Pet         | snake     | horse | hedgehog |

