.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
House: ranch-style, modern, futuristic
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill, montecristo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, black, pink
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, mechanic, software-developer
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, train
 1. the software-developer is the person who likes black##1
 2. the software-developer is the montecristo-smoker##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the videographer##1
 4. the person driving the car is between the modern house and the ranch-style house##2
 5. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
 6. the modern house is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the software-developer is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| House      | ranch-style   | futuristic    | modern         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Cigar   | bongani  | montecristo  | dunhill     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Color   | pink      | black   | orange    |
| Job           | videographer        | software-developer      | mechanic         |
| Transport         | roller | car  | train |

