The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, tulip, dahlia
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald, grey
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bolivar, fonseca
 1. the pilot is the person who likes emerald##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the police-officer##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the person who likes emerald##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the train is between the person who growstulip and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who growstulip is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the right of the pilot##1
11. the person who growstulip is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Job          | police-officer      | pilot      | designer      |
