The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, sailing
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, malaysian
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, taxi, scooter
 1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 2. the modern house is the malaysian##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person traveling to new-york and the modern house##2
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing go##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| House      | modern | gothic-revival           | ranch-style      |
