 7. the person driving the bike is between the person who likes white and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who likes white##1

