The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, project-manager, accountant
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, electronic, rock
3 different games are played: billiard, chess, whist
 1. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the accountant is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person playing whist is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing billiard##1
10. the accountant is on the left of the project-manager##1
11. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | april | may      | september      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| City   | colone  | liverpool     | marseilles |
| Job           | videographer        | accountant | project-manager     |
| Music-Genre         | metal    | rock | electronic   |
| Game     | chess        | whist        | billiard   |

