The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinesesy, dog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
House: wooden, colonial, craftsman
1. the pakistani is on the left of the musician##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the owner of the hedgehog and the manager##2
5. the person who growsorchid is between the musician and the person who's birthday is in june##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the pakistani##1
8. the wooden house is on the left of the colombian##1
9. the owner of the chinesesy is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
