6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the electrician is the cottage house##1
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

