The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, gospel, ambient
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, poppy
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, february, june
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, dancing
1. the person playing monopoly is the fan of ambient##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person playing go and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the fisherman is the fan of metal##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the person who growssunflower is between the fan of metal and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game      | chess    | monopoly       | go      |
| Music-Genre          | metal   | ambient   | gospel  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Flower   | dahlia   | sunflower     | poppy  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Birthday         | february | april   | june  |
| Hobby     | hiking    | dancing     | magic-tricks      |

 